  "intro": "<h2 class=\"section-heading\">Pinedale to Bolder in the morning</h2>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"../img/tourdivide/day19/day19pic01.JPG\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:85%\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"caption text-muted\">This guy had a nice view of the surrounding RV park\n                                    </a>\n                                </span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPinedale had been a good stop but I realized in the morning I should have continued on to Bolder.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThey had full services and the ride was flat to down for eight miles. This would have saved me a bit\n\t\t\t\t\t\tduring the second part of the day when I took the roller coaster from South Pass to Atlantic City.\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>",
